data.description: PROPERTY BEING SOLD "AS IS". Welcome to this charming all-brick, one-story ranch home in South Holland, IL, featuring: 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, an oversized 2-car garage, and large backyard perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. This property is conveniently located close to schools and transportation. We are looking at a well-maintained home situated in a desirable neighborhood. This house offers easy access to various amenities including shopping centers, providing a variety of retail and dining options, the I94 & 294 expressways for quick commutes. This could be your perfect home upon completing whatever repairs are needed.
